solitonic solutions. In viscous relativistic hydrodynamics we have\nsecond order patial derivatives which physically represent dissipation terms.\nWe present numerical solutions and their corresponding algorithms for the cases\nwhere the equations are not integrable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Dec 2012 17:29:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-09"}
